                        <ns0:remarks>The ACTRIS IA in FP7 (2011-2015) project was finished in April 2015.
This project integrated the existing research infrastructures (EUSAAR, EARLINET, CLOUDNET, and a new trace gases network component) into a single coordinated framework. The project was funded within the EC 7th Framework Programme under "Research Infrastructures for Atmospheric Research".
ICARE (https://www.icare.univ-lille.fr/) contributes with the production and provision of satellite data that complements the ACTRIS ground-based data catalogue</ns0:remarks>
